{"tid":1913450,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中央候補委員官慶去世 網絡瘋傳是華春瑩丈夫","createTime":"2020-03-06T19:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T22:38:50.000Z","uid":165361,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2a67ff2983a63d8f8a1df6fa7a9e17d733fe064e","tid":1913450,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T19:51:37.000Z","msg":"中央候補委員官慶去世 網絡瘋傳是華春瑩丈夫<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/3/6/n11920481.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F3%2F6%2Fn11920481.htm&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=ed9507eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/3/6/n11920481.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n3 月 6 日，中國建築集團有限公司官網發布訃告：集團原黨組書記、董事長官慶於 2020 年 3 月 6 日因病醫治無效在北京逝世，終年 55 歲。<br />\n<br />\n訃告還稱，根據家屬意願，官慶的喪事從簡，不舉行送別儀式。<br />\n<br />\n公開資料顯示，官慶長期在建築央企工作，曾任中國建築股份有限公司副總裁，中國建築工程總公司總經理，中國建築工程總公司董事長、黨組書記，中國建築股份有限公司董事長、總裁等重要職務。目前是中共第十九屆中央候補委員。<br />\n<br />\n官慶去世引發關注，是因為網上傳出官慶是中共外交部發言人華春瑩的老公，立刻成為網上熱議的話題。<br />\n<br />\n在大陸微博上，官慶去世的消息後面，有著大量網友的跟貼，不少內容指向華春瑩：「華春瑩老公，怪不得發言人換人了」，「腦癌去世，外交部發言人華春瑩老公」。這些跟貼至今都沒被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n今年 2 月 24 日，中共外交部新聞司副司長趙立堅以新任發言人的身分首次現身，華春瑩對現場媒體做介紹。之後的記者發布會都是由趙主持。<br />\n<br />\n中共外交部官網的記錄顯示，華春瑩截至目前最後一次主持記者會是 2 月 7 日。<br />\n<br />\n在百度百科上，2018 年也曾有帖子稱官慶是華春瑩的老公。不過因為中共內部都是黑箱，目前還無法證實上述說法的準確性<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------<br />\n好多新聞都有講佢去世,不過無提係華春瑩老公<br />\n好多人留言話佢係華春瑩老公<br />\nRAP<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b444b4d05cecba525264516529dd5b2a93147e","tid":1913450,"uid":278765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T19:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0bhk8U6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0bhk8U6.gif&h=a4fd89b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"563b10afbb3875cbc4eb6883bf0296575bd3cdd9","tid":1913450,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T20:00:18.000Z","msg":"抵啦！"},{"pid":"d0fae1bcd8ac3e49aeb2489575059a539cadaecb","tid":1913450,"uid":173191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T20:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e53dd8a5eb83df0163bfea58217941904706460","tid":1913450,"uid":278765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T20:03:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PZcw9NFgU4E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPZcw9NFgU4E&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=a2a15d6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PZcw9NFgU4E</a>"},{"pid":"9b8e0619975ddacbf47b4a15f79e27608772c105","tid":1913450,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T20:29:37.000Z","msg":"冇所謂啦 還有黨"},{"pid":"720388dfb05ac180c71f49c18f573e0a5d6d04f8","tid":1913450,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4e53dd8a5eb83df0163bfea58217941904706460","tid":1913450,"uid":278765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T20:03:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PZcw9NFgU4E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPZcw9NFgU4E&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=a2a15d6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PZcw9NFgU4E</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T20:32:07.000Z","msg":"好正, 笑9官慶係keeper<br />\n華大媽比各級領導一層一層砌上去"},{"pid":"14efdc733d6511a4aa8d155d688de95ca6145ce9","tid":1913450,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T20:32:11.000Z","msg":"睇住老婆個樣 短二三十年命都係幸福"},{"pid":"cdfa3cfe24cbcec3d15e4c4c6a841bf9088983b6","tid":1913450,"uid":276821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T20:32:22.000Z","msg":"死唔重要，重要傳到幾多官"},{"pid":"5370acd39f25d607f0608d069e6a0bafdc87f71a","tid":1913450,"uid":342136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-